<BaseLayout title="Thermal Swimming at Grutas de Tolantongo — 36°C Waters in Limestone Rock" description="Thermal swimming at Tolantongo: bathing in 36°C geothermal waters inside grottoes, pools and thermal river. The unique experience of Grutas de Tolantongo in Hidalgo." canonical="/en/activities/thermal-swimming/" schema={schema} lang="en">
